			<h1>Kitco Privacy Policy</h1>
		
		
	
			<h1 style="margin: 0in 0in 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 27px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Privacy Policy</h1> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 16px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;">September 23, 2010<p></p></span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 10pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><b><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Kitco respects your privacy.<p></p></span></b></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">All personal information held or collected by Kitco is protected under the Province of Quebec<span>Â </span><i>An Act Respecting the Protection of Personal Information in the Private Sector</i>.<p></p></span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">This means we will never willfully disclose individually identifiable information about our customers to any third party without the customer's consent. Your personal information will be disclosed to Kitco for the purposes of maintaining your account with Kitco.<p></p></span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><b><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Privacy Philosophy</span></b><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;"><p></p></span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Kitco respects your privacy. Kitco does not sell, rent, or loan any identifiable information regarding its customers to any third party. Any information you give us is held with the utmost care and security, and will not be used in ways to which you have not consented. </span><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">subject line.<p></p></span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><b><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Use of Information Gathered<p></p></span></b></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Kitco will not collect any personal information about individuals except when specifically and knowingly provided by such individuals to create an account and perform transactions with Kitco, or when required by law (such as anti money laundering and anti terrorism acts in Canada, the<span>Â </span></span><em><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Proceeds of Crime (Money Laundering) and Terrorist Financing Act</span></em><em><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; font-style: normal;"><span>Â </span>and in the United States, the<span>Â </span></span></em><em><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Bank Secrecy Act</span></em><em><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; font-style: normal;"><span>Â </span>and the<span>Â </span></span></em><em><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Patriot Act)</span></em><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">. Examples of such information are: name, postal address, e-mail address, phone number, identification card and credit card information. This information is needed to complete your orders and to allow Kitco to contact you should there be a problem with the account opening process or with a transaction. This is the minimum we need to serve you to the best of our ability. Kitco may share non-personal aggregate, or summary, information regarding its customers with partners or other third parties, but Kitco does not sell or share any information at the individual customer level. Your IP address is maintained for administrative and technical purposes only.<p></p></span></p> <p style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Please note that<span>Â </span></span><span style="line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">failure to provide any of the required information may cause a delay in the approval process or result in rejection of a Customer's account application<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">.<p></p></span></span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 18px; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;"><p>Â </p></span></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><b><span st